<div class="container mt-3">
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <%= render 'layouts/alerts' %>
    <h1 class="h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal">About Us</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8 justify-content-centre lead">
      <div class="row">
        Welcome to HomeGig, your number one source for all Remote Work. We're dedicated to giving you the very best
        support, with a focus on transparency, hard work, and efficiency.
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        Founded in 2019, HomeGig has come a long way from its beginnings in ECE444. When
        it first started out, the drive to develop an intuitive platform for contracted works drove them to create a
        community so that HomeGig can offer you
        efficient and robust services. We now serve customers all over the world, and are thrilled that we're able to
        turn our passion into this website.
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions
        or
        comments, please don't hesitate to <%= link_to "contact us", "/contactus" %>.
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        Sincerely,
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        HomeGig Team
      </div>
    </div>
